title: Digital Puppet Masters Tournament Series - 1v1

embed.description: Welcome to the Digital Puppet Masters Tournament Series. This tournament is a single elimination 1v1 event.

body:
Just here to let people know I will be running a 1v1 single elimination tournament on weekend. All players from Oceania are welcome to register and compete. I am offering a $10 gift card to the winner. 

Registration is now open. For more information follow the link above. 

If you have any questions I can be contacted directly on https://discord.gg/4fYdqnU via VOIP or text message.
